{"tid":213860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝 賢 問 婷 婷：謝 洛 美 維 拿 邊 個 黎？","createTime":"2017-04-23T11:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T18:28:21.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21310ab35ea597fa62f6572896a039fe244fe36d","tid":213860,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"謝婷婷前晚出席品牌活動，剛巧父親謝賢路過附近，順道入場跟女兒合照，問到謝賢會否想婷婷早日結婚，向來風趣的他笑說：「叫佢快啲結婚啦！咁老仲唔嫁做乜！」至於有否見過婷婷男友謝洛美維拿（Jeremy Renner）？他竟反問﹕「邊個嚟？」婷婷即指父親並不認識對方。她續透露下周將到上海一個月拍攝電影《歐洲攻略》，至於謝洛美屆時會否探班，她即爆對方亦身在亞洲工作，問到見面是否相當方便，她笑說：「亞洲都好大嘅。（有冇帶佢畀媽咪見？）未。（大家係咩關係？）了解中。（畀佢幾多分？）高分，但冇一名詞、冇數字。諗緊自己一個定拍拖，之前喺洛杉磯做咗鍾意做嘅嘢，好有滿足感，如果我做女朋友會好投入。（佢等你？）我想，如果佢OK。（問佢？）唔會問啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20170423/photo/0423-00282-019b3.jpg?t=1492947992938\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170423%2Fphoto%2F0423-00282-019b3.jpg%3Ft%3D1492947992938&h=2db32ea0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dd0521622c22fe0d3a0474a75c33e9613506529","tid":213860,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"個袋俗撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b693675b0ff2749ed8655a16453201f7035d5955","tid":213860,"uid":98322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"女版謝賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726423e2de9bbafe743c277a670c16a5c6b22e36","tid":213860,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"個鬼佬係荷李活明星 , 當謝婷婷係雞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d4b66efd067fa339803b504316898935ac053b","tid":213860,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85a3e53290a1e0b68f56156f7c0bcca0a90935bf","tid":213860,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"